<paragraph id="8BBC0439FFBCFFA017EEF87729B6F7BA" blockId="3.[136,1452,1958,2093]" pageId="3" pageNumber="262">
Since the application of names of taxa at the rank of family or below is determined by means of nomenclatural 
<typeStatus id="54B8BA9BFFBCFFA01216F87628FAF856" box="[1392,1451,1959,1985]" pageId="3" pageNumber="262">types</typeStatus>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EF9279C8FFBCFFA017E9F81B2C3DF873" author="Turland, N. J. &amp; Wiersema, J. H. &amp; Barrie, F. R. &amp; Greuter, W. &amp; Hawksworth, D. L. &amp; Herendeen, P. S. &amp; Knapp, S. &amp; Kusber, W. - H. &amp; Li, D. - Z. &amp; Marhold, K. &amp; May, T. W. &amp; McNeill, J. &amp; Monro, A. M. &amp; Prado, J. &amp; Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F." box="[143,364,1994,2021]" pageId="3" pageNumber="262" refId="ref15756" refString="Turland, N. J., Wiersema, J. H., Barrie, F. R., Greuter, W., Hawksworth, D. L., Herendeen, P. S., Knapp, S., Kusber, W. - H., Li, D. - Z., Marhold, K., May, T. W., McNeill, J., Monro, A. M., Prado, J., Price, M. J. &amp; Smith, G. F. (2018) International Code of Nomenclature for algae, fungi, and plants (Shenzhen Code) adopted by the Nineteenth International Botanical Congress Shenzhen, China, July 2017. Koeltz Botanical Books, Oberreifenberg. [Regnum Vegetabile 159]. https: // doi. org / 10.12705 / Code. 2018" type="journal volume" year="2018">
Turland 
<emphasis id="B977D82BFFBCFFA01796F81A2C73F873" box="[240,290,1994,2020]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="262">et al</emphasis>
. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
: Art.7.1), clarity on the lectotypification of the name 
<taxonomicName id="4C037FBAFFBCFFA014A5F81A294AF873" box="[963,1051,1995,2020]" class="Gymnostomatea" family="Spathidiidae" genus="Bryophyllum" kingdom="Chromista" order="Spathidiida" pageId="3" pageNumber="262" phylum="Ciliophora" rank="species" species="rosei">
<emphasis id="B977D82BFFBCFFA014A5F81A294AF873" box="[963,1051,1995,2020]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="262">K. rosei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
facilitates a detailed comparison of 
<emphasis id="B977D82BFFBCFFA017EEF83E2CE0F79F" box="[136,433,2030,2056]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="262">Perrier de la Bâthie 11825</emphasis>
with specimens, both preserved and living, previously associated with names published for species that are included in 
<emphasis id="B977D82BFFBCFFA016D8F7C22C80F7BB" box="[446,465,2067,2092]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="262">
<collectionCode id="ED129CFCFFBCFFA016D8F7C22C80F7BB" box="[446,465,2067,2092]" country="United Kingdom" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15867" name="Royal Botanic Gardens" pageId="3" pageNumber="262" type="Herbarium">K</collectionCode>
</emphasis>
. subg. 
<taxonomicName id="4C037FBAFFBCFFA01544F7C32FE2F7BB" box="[546,691,2066,2092]" class="Gymnostomatea" family="Spathidiidae" genus="Bryophyllum" kingdom="Chromista" order="Spathidiida" pageId="3" pageNumber="262" phylum="Ciliophora" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B977D82BFFBCFFA01544F7C32FE2F7BB" box="[546,691,2066,2092]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="262">Bryophyllum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and that share at least some of its character states.
</paragraph>
